{"tid":61352,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"大家有冇好似我咁嘅經歷 點樣走出去？求下你教吓我呀","createTime":"2016-12-31T07:19:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-01T15:12:57.000Z","uid":71395,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"01097929fe7a8781cdab420bd7b46c8cd2d3b405","tid":61352,"uid":71395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T07:19:34.000Z","msg":"曾經有一個人陪住我渡過左好多好多嘅難關<br />\n雖然唔叫做驚天動地 但起碼叫做刻骨銘心 <br />\n<br />\n依家得返我自己一個去捱過無數嘅晚上<br />\n雖然唔叫做好想返轉頭好想搵返佢 但起碼見到一啲有關佢嘅嘢都會諗起佢掛住佢 <br />\n<br />\n依一年黎 遇到過臭雞 亦都遇到好多好好嘅人<br />\n但慢慢自己喺度發現 即使一個人幾好幾好 我都會講出佢唔好嘅地方 話佢唔適合自己 話同佢唔會夾<br />\n但原來慢慢發現 <br />\n原來自己追求嘅唔係佢嘅影子 <br />\n原來自己追求嘅係佢<br />\n<br />\n我知道我同佢唔會再有可能 <br />\n唔會再考慮同返佢一齊<br />\n但係我可以點樣走出去？<br />\n有冇人可以教吓我"},{"pid":"354fdd34303941318823d39282a5ceb808b1a569","tid":61352,"uid":71395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T07:20:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6d9100344a158e2322f76a8e9daa2cd4f3c08c2","tid":61352,"uid":71395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T07:24:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7db1379e0e1b51c27a9425ea01110f9c9acec44b","tid":61352,"uid":57062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T07:26:16.000Z","msg":"劉明學野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d9cb565aa074cbac745ff7cb92b8254096f28d0","tid":61352,"uid":71395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T07:27:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>劉明學野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"389017d9371d9f5ff56e5aea2f755cf1bc8b1a34","t